Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.78,0:20:51.75,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}哦  其实这次真的是他\N{\fs40\b0}Oh, yeah. He's truth in' it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.76,0:20:53.69,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}所以对于这个引力干扰  你有什么见解吗？\N{\fs40\b0}So what can you tell me about this gravitational disturbance?
