Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.55,0:22:17.95,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}这太打击了  真的太打击盖瑞了\N{\fs40\b0}It's crushing, just absolute so crushing for this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.85,0:22:27.95,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}他给她发了五年的消息\N{\fs40\b0}He's been sending these messages to her for five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.65,0:22:40.45,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}他以为她收到了那些消息\N{\fs40\b0}He thinks that she's been getting them,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.45,0:22:43.05,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}但是并不知道为什么她不回信\N{\fs40\b0}doesn't really know she hasn't been responding though.
