Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.95,0:22:56.95,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}重新想一下要怎么和这个真人展开联系\N{\fs40\b0}and figure out how to actually make connection with the real person.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.25,0:23:08.75,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我体会不到这种感觉  这种事从来没在我身上发生过\N{\fs40\b0}I can't relate to that, that's never happened to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.25,0:23:12.55,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}至于月饼  他总是一副“Chookity”的样子\N{\fs40\b0}With Mooncake, he was always kind of like "Chookity".
